      <title>以色列称除非哈马斯被摧毁，否则不会永久停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/israel-says-biden-s-latest-gaza-peace-plan-is-only-part-of-story</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡重申，在该国提出的条件得到满足（包括消灭该激进组织）之前，加沙对哈马斯的战争不会永久停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/israel-says-biden-s-latest-gaza-peace-plan-is-only-part-of-story</guid>
